query:
SELECT 
  tc.id as inspection_id,
  tc.taskId,
  tc.templateId,
  tc.status,
  COUNT(cir.id) as item_count,
  COUNT(cti.id) as template_items_count
FROM taskChecklists tc
LEFT JOIN checklistItemResults cir ON cir.taskChecklistId = tc.id
LEFT JOIN checklistTemplateItems cti ON cti.templateId = tc.templateId
GROUP BY tc.id, tc.taskId, tc.templateId, tc.status
HAVING item_count = 0 AND template_items_count > 0
LIMIT 20;
